children.name: Automation Rate Create Process Order grouped by Business Line Short

dataSource.query:
SELECT (COUNT (EVENT_NAME) FILTER (WHERE "Event Created By User Type" NOT IN ('Dialog'))) / (COUNT (EVENT_NAME)) * 100 AS "% Automation Create Process Order", 
COUNT(EVENT_NAME) AS "# Create Process Order",
"Division"
FROM FLATTEN(THIS_PROCESS)
WHERE EVENT_NAME = 'Create Process Order'
-- GROUP BY 2
ORDER BY 1 desc

children.name: # Finished PO without deletion flag over time

dataSource.query:
SELECT DATE_TRUNC('month', (SELECT FIRST (end_time))) AS "Month", COUNT (CASE_ID)
as Cases
FROM THIS_PROCESS
WHERE "Actual Finish Date" IS NOT NULL AND "Deletion Flag" IS NULL
ORDER BY 1 ASC NULLS FIRST
FILL timeseries('MONTH'), NULL

children.name: # Finished PO without deletion flag grouped by Business Line Short

dataSource.query:
SELECT COUNT (CASE_ID) AS "# Process Orders", "Division"
FROM THIS_PROCESS
WHERE "Actual Finish Date" IS NOT NULL AND "Deletion Flag" IS NULL
GROUP BY 2
ORDER BY 1 desc

SELECT count(case_id) FILTER (WHERE event_name MATCHES ('Partially confirmed')) FROM THIS_PROCESS

children.name: ⌀ Create Process  → Set Deletion Flag with partial confirmation

dataSource.query:
SELECT avg(
(Select last(end_time) Filter(
Where event_name IN ('Deletion Flag')))
-
(Select first(end_time) Filter(
Where event_name IN ('Create Process Order')))
) 
FILTER (WHERE event_name MATCHES ('Partially confirmed')) FROM THIS_PROCESS

children.name: ⌀ Create Process  → Set Deletion Flag with no partial confirmation

dataSource.query:
SELECT avg(
(Select last(end_time) Filter(
Where event_name IN ('Deletion Flag')))
-
(Select first(end_time) Filter(
Where event_name IN ('Create Process Order')))
) 
FILTER (WHERE NOT event_name MATCHES ('Partially confirmed')) FROM THIS_PROCESS

children.name: ⌀ Basic End Date - Basic Start Date

dataSource.query:
SELECT avg(
"Basic Finish Date"  - "Basic Start Date" 
) 
FROM THIS_PROCESS

FROM FLATTEN(THIS_PROCESS)

ORDER BY 1 ASC NULLS FIRST

SELECT count(event_name) as "Confirmations" , "Division",

"Basic Finish Date"  - "Basic Start Date"
